Which application in IBM SmartCloud Control Desk V7.5 is used to link an existing software
image Configuration Item (CI) in the CMDB to the Definitive Media Library (DML)
repository?
A. CI
B. DML
C. Changes
D. Releases
Answer: D

When an Asset and a Configuration Item (CI) are linked they provide a unified
representation of the IT resource and can be managed together. At which two lifecycle
stages should an Asset be linked to a CI?
A. Planning
B. Retirement
C. Acquisition
D. Deployment
E. Maintenance
Answer: A,D

What are two ways to resolve a reconciliation result?
A. use the Create Problem action to investigate the cause
B. use the Create Deployment to update the actual Configuration Item (CI) values
C. use the Update CI with Actual CI Value action to update the CI attributes
D. use the Copy Previous Reconciliation Result action to update the CI attributes
E. use the Update CI with Actual CI Value action to update the actual CI attributes
Answer: A,E
